{"tid":1963666,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港迪士尼副總裁以上行政人員　本月起減薪二至三成","createTime":"2020-04-08T09:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T10:04:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac09ff95b30206170a1953b9b42e37ab168e865","tid":1963666,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:49:56.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】香港迪士尼高級行政人員本月起減薪兩成至三成。<br />\n<br />\n香港迪士尼樂園發言人指，因為新型冠狀病毒疫情，樂園由1月26日起暫時關閉，酒店服務亦有調整。<br />\n<br />\n由於重開日期仍未明朗，樂園須採取進一步措施，本月起所有副總裁職級以上的行政管理人員，暫時減薪兩成至三成，樂園亦要求所有全職演藝人員，每周放一天無薪假。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=387177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387177&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBb9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=d1c7ae9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387177&h=0968447c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=387177</a>"},{"pid":"634b83a369ae5a386a289c3fc7393ac9f8b69d05","tid":1963666,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:04:16.000Z","msg":"咁少？無營運直情cut一半"}]}